text.tspan: A decade box is a simple instrument for easily
changing values of passive components during
prototyping. Our ResPot is a fancy resistor
decade box where the values are set manually
using a wire. Connecting the individual pieces

tspan.tspan: in series results in the desired resistance.

text.tspan: We supply five ResPot boards and
ten each of six resistor values: 1Ω,
Use ResPot with a breadboard for
